                Using pre-trained Random Forest Regressor (v2.4) trained on 10k historical records.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div className="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold flex items-center gap-1">
                <CheckCircle size={14} />
                READY
